To bite another human being is an animalistic instinct and is, quite frankly, inhumane.

For someone to lower themselves to that level on a football pitch is wholly unacceptable.

Following Luis Suarez's latest alleged attempt to take a bite out of an opponent, FIFA must be strong and throw the book at him. They must act as the IRB have on many occasions in rugby.

